Introduction

Y TEEN (Korean: Y틴; Japanese: Yティーン) was a fourteen-member project group under Starship Entertainment. It consisted of all seven members of MONSTA X and seven from WJSN. They debuted on August 6, 2016 with the single "Do Better".

The group was a collaboration with the mobile company KT to promote as CF models for their 'Y Teen' phone plan.
